      "contentText": "2026 Joe Rossi Umpires Hall of Fame Presents - The Umpire's Cup IV Days Hours Minutes Seconds Check back soon for photos of this special event. The Joe Rossi Umpires Hall of Fame Golf Tournament is a long‑standing tradition bringing golfers together for a fun, relaxed day of golf in support of the Joe Rossi Umpires Hall of Fame. This event celebrates community, camaraderie, and the lasting legacy of all who have contributed so much to the game of baseball in Colorado. Register Now Event Details 📅 Date: Saturday, June 27, 2026 ⏰ Time: 8:00 a.m. 💲 Entry Fee: $130 per golfer 📍 Location: Applewood Golf Club 14001 W. 32nd Ave. Golden, CO 80401 Registration Register Now Raffle Tickets & Mulligans Make your day on the course even more fun while supporting the Joe Rossi Umpires Hall of Fame. Save time in line during check in and purchase your raffle tickets and mulligans in advance! Click to Purchase Click to Purchase Can't Make It... Donate Instead! If you’re unable to attend the tournament, you can still support the Joe Rossi Umpires Hall of Fame. Choose a one-time donation or become a monthly supporter to help preserve the legacy of baseball officiating in Colorado. Support The Hall of Fame Share Blocksy: Share Box",
