      "contentText": "2026 Colorado Baseball Umpires Joe Rossi Hall of Fame Induction Banquet Days Hours Minutes Seconds Check back soon for photos of this special event. It is time again for one of the highlights of the high school baseball season — the 2026 annual Colorado Baseball Umpires Joe Rossi Hall of Fame Induction Banquet. This special event is held the day before the CHSBUA Master Clinic and honors the exceptional individuals who have contributed so much to the game of baseball in Colorado. Please give serious consideration to attending this banquet to celebrate and show gratitude to our new inductees. Terry Angell George Demetriou Fred Zuercher Don’t forget to include your significant others and friends in your registration! Register Now Event Details Date : Saturday, January 31, 2026 Time : 31, 2026 Location: Holiday Inn Denver–Lakewood 7390 W. Hampden Ave., Lakewood, CO 80227 Hotel Accommodations A special room rate is available at the Holiday Inn Denver–Lakewood. Make your reservation by calling (303) 980-9200 and using GROUP CODE: JRH before January 16, 2026 . Registration $43 before December 14, 2025 $50 from December 15, 2025 to January 25, 2026 Business casual attire is recommended. Please include significant others and friends in your registration. Register Now Share Blocksy: Share Box",
